==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Masker
<hw>Mask"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who wears a mask;
one who appears in disguise at a masquerade.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Masker</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Masker
<hw>Mask"er</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To confuse; to stupefy.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Holland.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Maskery</ent>⟦br⟧
